title: Molly Moo Cow And Rip Van Winkle ( Van Beuren 1935)

sources.title: Molly Moo Cow And Rip Van Winkle ( Van Beuren 1935)
sources.description: Molly Moo - Cow  discovers some dwarfs having fun drinking beer and bowling near a sleeping  Rip Van Winkle . After the dwarfs leave,  Molly  joins in on the fun only only to become drunk and wake up  Rip Van Winkle .
